This is a basic 4 I2S MEMS mic testing code for teensy 4.1 to check if the connection are correct or not.
It shows the Live Audio Input from the MICS onto the Serial Plotter of Arduino IDE. 
Pin Configs. are :
Mics     Teensy 4.1
Vcc ---> 3V3
GND ---> GND
SCK ---> Pin 21
WS  ---> Pin 20
SD  ---> Pin 6 = Mic 1 & 2  and  Pin 8 = Mic 3 & 4.
L/R ---> Mic 1 = GND , Mic 2 = Vcc , Mic 3 = GND , Mic 4 = Vcc
